	Date: Tuesday, 22 October 2019
	Venue: National Assembly Chamber, Parliament
	Time: 14:00
	
	Journalists and photographers who do not have Parliamentary media access permits and wish to cover the National Assembly sitting should send their details (full name, ID/passport number and name of the media house) to Mlindi Mpindi on 081 716 7329 or 021 403 2340 or mmpindi@parliament.gov.za.
	
